<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 14:07:51 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>超过 110 名记者在加沙被杀。以色列同行保持沉默</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</link><description>太多的以色列记者将某种程度的罪责归咎于他们在加沙的同行——甚至认为他们是应该死的努赫巴部队成员</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:33:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-08-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/over-110-journalists-have-been-killed-in-gaza-their-israeli-colleagues-keep-silent/00000191-2c36-daed-a3ff-af3f92620000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩担心伊朗和真主党的反应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</link><description>边境地区的人们正在储存食物和水，等待以色列对贝鲁特的猛烈袭击。 “哈尼亚被暗杀后，我们意识到我们不能留在黎巴嫩。我们告诉孩子们，情况不安全，我们必须离开。”一位正在回国的法国妇女说道。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:19:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/lebanon-waits-in-fear-for-iran-and-hezbollahs-response/00000191-2c88-d1b4-a399-7cae8b7f0000</guid></item><item><title>“新犹太人”的象征如何最终被装进盒子里——并陷入法律纠纷</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</link><description>以色列博物馆展出的伊扎克·丹齐格 (Yitzhak Danziger) 的《尼姆罗德》(Nimrod) 新照片引发了法律和道德争议，引发了一个问题：一件艺术品真正属于谁？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 12:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/life/2024-08-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/how-the-symbol-of-the-new-jew-ended-up-in-a-box-and-in-a-legal-dispute/00000191-2bd0-d2a9-a5dd-3fd966b60000</guid></item><item><title>美国驻日本大使因未邀请以色列而缺席长崎原子弹追悼会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</link><description>该市市长表示，鉴于国际社会对战争的反应，人们担心仪式上会出现抗议、破坏或袭击。加拿大、法国、德国、意大利和英国也发函表达了对以色列被排除在外的共同担忧</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 10:55:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/u-s-ambassador-to-japan-to-skip-a-bomb-memorial-service-because-israel-was-not-invited/00000191-2c62-d7d8-a7bb-ee7a3c1a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方突击搜查外交部，怀疑在发放外交护照方面存在不法行为——包括向内塔尼亚胡的儿子发放外交护照</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</link><description>据两名官员称，正在调查的其中一本护照是给总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡的儿子亚伊尔·内塔尼亚胡的护照</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 09:20:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/police-raid-foreign-ministry-on-suspicion-of-illegally-granting-diplomatic-passports/00000191-2c19-d32b-ad9f-3d3b58c50000</guid></item><item><title>海法居民担心真主党的罢工将针对该市的危险材料港口区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</link><description>在真主党领导人纳斯鲁拉提到海法是火箭袭击的潜在目标后，尽管以色列军队下令减少石化产品库存，但其居民仍担心会发生危险材料事件</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 08:59:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/haifa-residents-fear-hezbollah-strike-will-target-citys-hazardous-materials-port-area/00000191-2bc2-d1b4-a399-7fe6b2ce0000</guid></item><item><title>AIPAC 的另一场胜利：韦斯利·贝尔 (Wesley Bell) 和 850 万美元击败“小队”成员科里·布什 (Cori Bush)</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</link><description>亲以色列游说团体的联合民主项目称赞这一结果“进一步证明亲以色列是两党的好政策和好政治”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:29:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/another-victory-for-aipac-wesley-bell-and-8-5-million-defeat-squad-member-cori-bush/00000191-2adb-d2a9-a5dd-3edb30180001</guid></item><item><title>西方列强日益关注俄罗斯与伊朗日益加强的合作</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</link><description>在有报道称俄罗斯正在向伊朗提供军事援助并试图向胡塞武装提供武器后，西方外交官发出了警报。一位外交官告诉《国土报》，“俄罗斯的介入让我们非常担心，以色列也应该担心”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:01:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/western-powers-increasingly-concerned-about-growing-russia-iran-cooperation/00000191-2911-d642-a9d5-bb51462b0000</guid></item><item><title>对于真主党来说，以色列痛苦的等待是其报复的一部分，但它仍然希望避免战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</link><description>哈桑·纳斯鲁拉周二在贝鲁特发表了激烈的演讲，但没有明确威胁爆发地区战争——他的组织及其伊朗赞助人显然仍在寻求避免这种情况</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 03:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/for-hezbollah-israels-agonizing-wait-is-part-of-its-revenge/00000191-2950-d642-a9d5-bb50d8a50000</guid></item><item><title>真主党和胡塞武装祝贺哈马斯新领导人辛瓦尔</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</link><description>戈兰地区委员会：以色列北部居民必须留在避难所附近，并尽量减少不必要的旅行 ■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，至少有 39,653 名巴勒斯坦人在加沙丧生 ■ 真主党声称对以色列北部的无人机袭击负责 ■ 以色列国防军，辛贝特称以色列战斗机袭击了黎巴嫩南部真主党军事基地</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 02:12:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article-live/nasrallah-nerve-racking-anticipation-part-of-hezbollah-response-goal-to-exhaust-israel/00000191-2a95-dcd6-abf7-7e975efc0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长告诉内塔尼亚胡：你的内阁工作程序有缺陷，损害公共利益</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</link><description>加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉（Gali Baharav-Miara）在给总理的信中表示，内阁秘书发布的法律意见超越了他的职权，“在安全领域产生了严重影响”</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 22:17:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-tells-netanyahu-your-cabinets-work-procedures-are-flawed-harm-the-public/00000191-293d-d1b4-a399-7dbf1ec20000</guid></item><item><title>特拉维夫官员拒绝赎罪日户外祈祷请求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-official-rejects-requests-for-yom-kippur-outdoor-prayer/00000191-28b0-d1b4-a399-7cb67ef60000</link><description>在居民和政界人士的强烈抗议之后，市政府发表了一份似乎与自己的裁决相矛盾的声明</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:54:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/tel-aviv-official-rejects-requests-for-yom-kippur-outdoor-prayer/00000191-28b0-d1b4-a399-7cb67ef60000</guid></item><item><title>美国-以色列摔跤手阿米特·埃洛尔在巴黎奥运会上夺得金牌</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-wrestler-amir-elor-strikes-gold-at-paris-olympics/00000191-2975-dcd6-abf7-7f77c7700000</link><description>这位 20 岁的父母出生于以色列移民家庭，成为在奥运会上赢得金牌的最年轻的美国摔跤手（无论男女）</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 21:04:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-08-07/ty-article/.premium/american-israeli-wrestler-amir-elor-strikes-gold-at-paris-olympics/00000191-2975-dcd6-abf7-7f77c7700000</guid></item><item><title>伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚被杀后，哈马斯任命加沙领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔为酋长</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</link><description>辛瓦尔曾担任加沙哈马斯领导人，也是10月7日事件的策划者，现在将担任该组织的最高政治领导人。这一任命被视为哈马斯向以色列、美国、人质协议调解人和巴勒斯坦公众发出的信息</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 20:02:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/hamas-names-gaza-leader-yahya-sinwar-as-chief-following-ismail-haniyeh-killing/00000191-290f-dcda-adf3-6d4f5a180000</guid></item><item><title>涉嫌虐待巴勒斯坦囚犯的士兵在测谎仪测试中撒谎；检方将逮捕期限延长至周日</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</link><description>这些士兵涉嫌情节严重的虐待行为、强奸情况下的鸡奸行为、侵犯权力和不当行为</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 19:33:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/soldiers-suspected-of-abusing-palestinian-prisoner-lied-on-polygraph-test/00000191-2868-d5e8-a397-fef831300000</guid></item><item><title>英国廉价航空公司 EasyJet 暂停以色列航班直至 2025 年春季</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</link><description>由于担心与伊朗和真主党发生重大冲突，易捷航空 (EasyJet) 在取消和暂停往返以色列航班的众多航空公司中名列前茅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/budget-u-k-airline-easyjet-suspends-israel-flights-until-spring-2025/00000191-28ee-d2a9-a5dd-3eff6e320000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军方称，被认为失踪的比尔哈·伊农 (Bilha Inon) 于 10 月 7 日被杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</link><description>据军方称，在她家附近发现的证据证实她是被谋杀的。伊农的家人于10月7日宣布了她被谋杀的消息，第二天开始哀悼她和她的丈夫雅科维</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:50:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-bilha-inon-considered-missing-was-killed-on-october-7/00000191-28de-d642-a9d5-bbdefeb30000</guid></item><item><title>华尔兹谈夏皮罗：美国准备好迎接一位犹太副总统了吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-06/ty-article/.highlight/walz-over-shapiro-will-america-ever-be-ready-for-a-jewish-vp/00000191-2838-d5e8-a397-fef8de350000</link><description>副总统卡马拉·哈里斯选择明尼苏达州州长蒂姆·沃尔兹作为她的竞选伙伴，而不是宾夕法尼亚州州长乔什·夏皮罗。无论沃尔兹的资历如何，最近发生的事件都会给许多美国犹太人留下苦涩的味道</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 18:39:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-08-06/ty-article/.highlight/walz-over-shapiro-will-america-ever-be-ready-for-a-jewish-vp/00000191-2838-d5e8-a397-fef8de350000</guid></item><item><title>性别中立的酸奶标志引发以色列网络文化战争风暴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/gender-neutral-yogurt-logo-sparks-israeli-internet-culture-war-firestorm/00000191-2874-d102-a39d-3c7467840000</link><description>以色列食品巨头施特劳斯为其广受欢迎的儿童酸奶杯“Dwarfs”推出了新标志，因此这个最初以男性形式书写的单词现在可以读作女性或男性。社交媒体上几乎立即爆发了对这一变化的强烈反对，许多用户呼吁抵制</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 17:39:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/gender-neutral-yogurt-logo-sparks-israeli-internet-culture-war-firestorm/00000191-2874-d102-a39d-3c7467840000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第305天：真主党主席表示伊朗不应该参与公开战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-305-iran-shouldnt-be-part-of-open-war-hezbollah-chief-says/00000191-2859-d2a9-a5dd-3e59bdec0000</link><description>真主党火箭弹和无人机对以色列北部的袭击造成三人受伤 ■ 戈兰和上加利利地区议会指示居民留在避难所附近 ■ 据报道，普京要求伊朗最高领导人在德黑兰对哈尼亚杀戮的回应中避免针对以色列平民 ■ 八名巴勒斯坦人丧生，其中包括四名青少年，在以色列国防军突袭、空袭约旦河西岸期间，巴勒斯坦官员表示 ■ 这是战争开始 305 天后您需要了解的内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 06 Aug 2024 16:22:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-08-06/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-305-iran-shouldnt-be-part-of-open-war-hezbollah-chief-says/00000191-2859-d2a9-a5dd-3e59bdec0000</guid></item></channel></rss>